{"tid":2036401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明天行動宗旨：保護自身安全為大前提下  向世界宣告  香港人唔會因為打壓  疫情而停止追求自由既步伐","createTime":"2020-05-26T12:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T17:43:01.000Z","uid":134033,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a16c83e09b06c147f11103dbb6dac840635b6e37","tid":2036401,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"聽朝出發前 諗好自己可以做到咩  要做到咩<br />\n<br />\n一切要以生命安全為先<br />\n<br />\n行動失敗就失敗 唔悔氣唔互屌唔分化<br />\n<br />\n唔戀戰 唔格硬來<br />\n<br />\n自由既道路係非常漫長  好多杖仲要打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家心知 立會基本上攻唔入<br />\n<br />\n好難阻到如此邪惡既極權勢力過法案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地重點係要重燃香港人抗爭既火焰<br />\n<br />\n唔會因為各種理由而變懶 變麻木  變到放棄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然  有手足遇到危難 必需全力協助同拯救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5f9c2bed4cd7ac2beef5fc3c7558191a75095e8","tid":2036401,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8299422432eb6dad65318f09cb8a33c8eff44fc7","tid":2036401,"uid":93084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"幫推，真係重中之重"},{"pid":"b18c0897c36b848b2db4e649cc71d389b1d469f8","tid":2036401,"uid":171204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa9604519e8b97274f614c86001bfe3df8377fe0","tid":2036401,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00f9b15cf5825a7b4c96853dff50f9394eb045b","tid":2036401,"uid":87189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"de4